The organizational six steps of the data analysis process
Ask
prepare
process
analyz
share
act.
Data ecosystem
The data ecosystem is a group of elements that interact with one another on order to produce, manage,store, 
organize, analyze and share data. The element includes hardware, software and the people who used them
 
