Analytical thinking
Identifying and defining any problem then solving it using data in an organized and step by step matter.
Key aspects of analytical thinking
1. Visualization(The graphical representation of information)
2. Stratgy (being stratgic when interacting huge amount of data to stay focused on solving problem)

